## Disclaimer

TruthGuard is designed to assist in identifying potentially false or misleading information. 
The system's outputs should be considered as indicators rather than definitive judgments. 
Users should always verify information through multiple reliable sources and exercise 
critical thinking when evaluating claims.

The developers of TruthGuard are not responsible for any decisions made based on the 
system's outputs, nor for any consequences arising from the use of this software.

